Configuration Platform SDK 9.0 API Reference

CfgOperationMode

Values

Mnemonic ID Flag Short Description Log Name Long Description
CFGOMNoOperationMode 0 0 'Unknown Operation Mode' NoOperationMode The value of corresponding parameter has not changed
CFGOMManual 1 0 'Manual' Manual Manual
CFGOMSchedule 2 0 'Scheduled' Schedule Scheduled

Top of Page

Comments

TT in value name means belonging to CfgOperationMode enumeration.

The CfgOperationMode is applicable for Configuration Library/Server release 5.1.5xx only.
